item.title: Indonesia Cendekia
item.description: Description This web application was designed for students who need test simulation for Science Olympiade preparation. Teacher account could create any tests and questions. Tests and question created can be access by students after they order the tests, finish the payment, and verified by admin. There are three types of question, such as: single choise, short answer, and essay. Not only Computer Base Test, this application also be equipped by free online course, news page, download page, etc.
